---
import WidgetWrapper from '~/components/ui/WidgetWrapper.astro';
---

<WidgetWrapper id="why-mallorn" containerClass="max-w-5xl py-20 md:py-28">
  <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Why Mallorn</p>
  <div class="mt-5 grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] md:items-start">
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl leading-tight text-heading sm:text-5xl">
        Better farming begins with a better understanding of biology.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-7 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
        Healthy agricultural ecosystems build soil, cycle nutrients, support biodiversity and resist disease. Yet the
        biological processes that make farms resilient are too often overlooked.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-l-2 border-accent pl-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-default">
      Mallorn Bio exists to understand those processes deeply—then turn that understanding into practical tools that
      help natural systems flourish.
    </div>
  </div>
</WidgetWrapper>
